text:
Tonight Kate and Leo, our dreamiest of dream duos, fulfilled all of our fantasies by walking the Oscars red carpet together―and being the CUTEST. Really, we squealed. Because LOOK:

Whispers. Giggles. Be still my beating heart.

"Do you want to get In-N-Out after this?"

"Leo, are you serious?"

"That is the ONLY thing I want."

"But wait, can we split fries too?"

"Of course. I know how to share. You're the one who wouldn't make room for me on that floating door."

"Okay, let's pose for some more photos and then sneak out the back"

"Smile. Burgers soon come."

Getty Images "You won. You really won."

Getty Images "I'm so happy for you."

Getty Images "Let's never let go."
